'''Uhur'qah''' was the industrial capital of [[Af'El/Legends|Af'El]].<ref name="SWAJ10:WBC">{{JournalCite|10|Wanted by Cracken (Star Wars Adventure Journal)}}</ref>

It was the location of several profitable mines owned by [[Toxis Metals]].<ref name="SWAJ10:WBC" />

